
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge,chrome=1" />

<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, minimum-scale=1, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=no, viewport-fit=cover">
<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no">

<!-- common ico -->
<link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/static/web/img/common/favicon.ico?v=20240610001">

<!-- common css -->
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/web/js/lib/spin.css?v=20230330001">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/web/css/dealer/2022/normalize.css?v=20230330001">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/web/css/dealer/2022/style.css?v=20230330001">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/web/css/dealer/2022/popup.css?v=20230330001">

<title>대출 근저당 해지 | iM캐피탈</title>
</head>
<body>
<div class="dim active"></div>
<div class="popup-layer active" id="dealerLayer">
    <div class="popup">
        <div class="inner">
            <div class="popup-head popup-text">
                <h1 tabindex="0">대출 근저당 해지</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="popup-close">
                <a href="javascript:;"><span class="blind">닫기</span></a>
            </div>
            <div class="popup-content">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="cont-table">
                        <table class="tbl-list view" style="width:100%;">
                            <caption>대출 근저당 해지 관련 세부 내역 테이블</caption>
		                    <colgroup>
		                        <col style="width:15%;">
		                        <col style="width:35%;">
		                        <col style="width:15%;">
		                        <col style="width:35%;">
		                    </colgroup>
                            <tbody>
                                <tr>
                                    <th>대출진행상태</th>
                                    <td>대출실행</td>
                                    <th>차량명</th>
                                    <td>모닝</td>
                                </tr>

                                <tr>
                                    <th>신청일자</th>
                                    <td>2025-08-14</td>
                                    <th>차종</th>
                                    <td>뉴 모닝(JA)</td>
                                </tr>

                                <tr>
                                    <th>대출상환예정일</th>
                                    <td>2026-11-10</td>
                                    <th>세부차종</th>
                                    <td>1.0 가솔린 스탠다드</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <th>대출승인금액</th>
                                    <td>10,000,000</td>
                                    <th>연식</th>
                                    <td>2022</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <th>대출신청금액</th>
                                    <td>9,000,000</td>
                                    <th>차량번호</th>
                                    <td>12가 1234</td>
                                </tr>
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="cont-table inp-align">
                        <table class="tbl-list view">
                            <caption>근저당 해지 관련 문자 수신받을 요청자 정보입력</caption>
		                    <colgroup>
		                        <col style="width:40%;">
		                        <col>
		                    </colgroup>
                            <tbody>
                                <tr>
                                    <th>근저당 해지 요청자</th>
                                    <td>
                                        <div class="inputbox">
                                            <input type="text" name="lVhclNo" id="lVhclNo" value="" title="근저당 해지 요청자 이름" placeholder="홍길동">
                                            <button class="btn-clear"></button>
                                        </div>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <th>요청자 연락처</th>
                                    <td>
                                        <div class="inputbox">
                                            <input type="text" name="lVhclNo" id="lVhclNo" value="" title="요청자 연락처" placeholder="예)010-1234-5678">
                                            <button class="btn-clear"></button>
                                        </div>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </tbody>
                        </table>
                        <p class="noti-txt">* 근저당 해지 관련 문자를 수신받을 요청자와 연락처를 작성해주세요.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="popup-btn">
            <button type="button" class="btn-confirm">근저당 해지 신청</button><!-- 비활성화인 경우 : disabled 클래스 추가 -->
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
